  "texts": [
    "Let a be a boundary condition on A(Σ) specified by a function on Bd(Σ) defined by a κ = a(S κ): m S κ → Irr(C).For given X, a, let i: Bd(Σ) → N be such that i κ = i(S κ) belongs to the index set of the chosen basis of C(X κ → ⊗a κ).",
    "The set of such functions i label the corresponding product basis ofC(X 1 → ⊗a 1) ⊗ • • • ⊗ C(X m → ⊗a m),and we refer to i as indexing the (X, a)-basis.",
    "For every m-tuple consisting of X 1,..., X m ∈ Irr Z(C), fix an orthonormal basis {α l } of Z(C)(1 → X 1 ⊗ • • • ⊗ X m) with respect to the trace inner product.Lemma A.1.",
    "The elements, e; X,a i,l:= Φ Σ (α l ⊗ wX 1 a 1 i 1 ⊗ • • • ⊗ w Xm a m im) (63)ranging over all X: Bd(Σ) → Irr Z(C), all boundary conditions a on Σ, all i indexing the (X, a)-basis, and all l indexing the basis of Z(C)(1 → X 1 ⊗ • • • ⊗ X m), form an orthonormal basis of A(Σ) w.r.t.",
    "the TQFT inner product."
